<div class="jsx-355086517 desc">LOCATION LOCATION! Top Rated schools! A 4-sided brick ranch with InLaw Suite located in the highly sought-after Norman downs. Boasting a New HVAC, upgraded kitchen, bathrooms, granite countertops, new hardwood floors, a newly built screened 3 season porch and a private backyard made to entertain this house is a perfect place to call home. The large eat-in Kitchen with built-in pantry opens to the family room w/cozy woodburning fireplace. Finished basement has a gas fireplace built-in bookcase, bedroom, bonus room and large media area. Norman Downes community was featured in the Atlanta Journal Constitution has a lake for fishing, a swimming pool and tennis court. Bunten Park is across the street and Gwinnett Arena is close by. The city of Duluth provides free outdoor movies, plays and concerts on the town green. This beautiful home is conveniently located near shopping malls, I-85, public transportation at Sugarloaf Mills. You will love the mature trees, rolling hills, and great neighbors. RANCHES LIKE THIS DON'T LAST LONG!</div>
